twitch_info.title: I Wanna Be The Animus in 14:54
twitch_info.description:
What a run, I'm not sure if i will ever attempt running Animus ever again after this.
2 Deaths in the entire run, 1 in Water and the other in Fire, costing me around 5 seconds in total. This run was perfect otherwise. Adding some dumb strats in like invert skip in Kale could bring the game down to sub 14:30.
